ISLAMABAD, Oct 17 (APP):National Command and Operation Center (NCOC) Sunday said that a fake video is circulating on social media regarding adverse effects of Covid Vaccination on schoolchildren.
In a Tweet, NCOC said that the video clip is three years old. Covid Vaccines are completely safe and can be administered to children as per Ministry of Health (MoH) guidelines, it added.
